query:
SELECT 
  prefecture, 
  city, 
  district,
  propertyType,
  tradePriceYen,
  area,
  buildingYear,
  pricePerSqm,
  (tradePriceYen / 10000) as tradePriceManYen
FROM transactions 
WHERE prefecture = '東京都' 
  AND city LIKE '%小平市%' 
  AND propertyType = 'house'
LIMIT 20;
